I18n module for drupal 6
	
this is a collection of modules to extend drupal core multilingual
capabilities and be able to build real life multilingual sites. some
features:

 * taxonomy translation (both, per language terms and translatable terms)
 * multilingual variables
 * multilingual blocks (control visibility per language and translate
   title and content)
 * language selection (when you switch the site language you'll see only
   the content for that language)